{
  "id": "RAW_bd3b148b",
  "title": "React、Next.js 曝出最高级别安全漏洞，尽快自查！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==&mid=2247536469&idx=1&sn=d38e0c1fee999b2bc4a95a9e13ab7953",
  "date": "2025-12-05 00:30:00",
  "author": "前端充电宝",
  "siteName": "前端充电宝",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a59377d5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FEO58xpw5UMONulk3fut1YYotogmXhicBg6B8U9yfAwibrGWGLUibnKIVcf1oVyQpSw1Njz9FHrAlbeNfWbpM3nswg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"word-wrap:break-word;overflow:hidden;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'SF Pro Text', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\">\n    <div style=\"height: auto;\">\n     <div>\n      <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"前端充电宝\" data-alias=\"FE-Charge\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EO58xpw5UMNJLOYUj7Uv3TSiaqDldeaxxhCosR00yDKGR9lvI4y9NOfG7ADJHfKEsKuVAFWgDPqLN5afgZGkbZg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"聚焦前端开发，探索AI新浪潮：宝藏工具×前沿动态×实战技巧，解锁前端新可能！\" data-id=\"MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">12 月 3 日，React 官方发布了一条非常罕见的安全公告：React Server Components（RSC）出现了一个</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">最高级别（CVSS 10）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的安全漏洞。Next.js 官方也同步发文确认受到影响。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你在用 React 19 + RSC，或者用 Next.js 的 App Router，请立刻检查版本。</span></strong></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">漏洞是什么？</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">RSC 在处理服务端请求时，需要把客户端发来的数据反序列化。本次问题就出在这里——</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">类型校验不严格</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，导致攻击者可以构造一个“伪 RSC 请求”，诱导服务器执行恶意代码。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">也就是说：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">不需要登录</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">不需要权限</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">只要能请求到你的接口</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">就有可能直接执行服务器端代码</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，这次漏洞才会被评为满分 10 分的严重程度。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">哪些版本受影响？</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">React 侧：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">react-server-dom-webpack</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/ parcel / turbopack（19.0 ~ 19.2 的部分版本）</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Next.js 侧：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">所有基于&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">App Router + RSC</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的版本基本都受影响</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">包括多数 15.x、16.x 稳定版</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">还有 14.3.0-canary.77 之后的部分 canary</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你的项目还停在 pages router，或者没有用到 RSC，本次风险较小。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么会这么严重？</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">RSC 引入了一套新的序列化协议，而这次的漏洞让攻击者能伪造这个协议的消息。只要你的应用在线上暴露了相关接口，风险就是“默认存在”的。更糟糕的是，很多团队可能根本没意识到自己启用了 RSC。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">怎么办？升级就是唯一修复方式</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">React 和 Next.js 已经发布了修复版本。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">React：</span></p>\n      <pre style=\"border-radius:6px 12px 6px 12px;border:1px solid #ebedf0;padding:16px;margin:16px 0;font-size:12.7969px;overflow-x:auto;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;line-height:1.6;margin-top:16px;\" tabindex=\"0\"><code style=\"border:none;padding:0;white-space:nowrap;display:block;\"><span line=\"1\"><span leaf=\"\">npm install react-server-dom-webpack@latest</span></span></code></pre>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Next.js：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">15.x → 升级到最新补丁（如 15.0.5、15.1.9 等）</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">16.x → 升级到 16.0.7</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用 14.3-canary 的，建议直接回稳定 14.x</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">官方明确说了：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">没有任何配置可以临时规避漏洞，只能升级。</span></strong></p>\n      <hr style=\"border:0;margin:24px 0;height:1px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">给你一个快速自查清单</span></h2>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"background-color:#0066ff;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;transform:translate(0px, -1px);font-weight:bold;width:20px;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;margin-right:10px;height:20px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">你的项目是否在使用 Next.js App Router？</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"background-color:#0066ff;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;transform:translate(0px, -1px);font-weight:bold;width:20px;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;margin-right:10px;height:20px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">2</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">依赖是否是 12 月 3 日前安装的 React 19？</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"background-color:#0066ff;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;transform:translate(0px, -1px);font-weight:bold;width:20px;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;margin-right:10px;height:20px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">3</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">lock 文件里是否出现受影响版本的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">react-server-dom-*</span></code><span leaf=\"\">？</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"background-color:#0066ff;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;transform:translate(0px, -1px);font-weight:bold;width:20px;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;margin-right:10px;height:20px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">4</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">CI 是否会使用旧缓存重新部署？</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"background-color:#0066ff;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;transform:translate(0px, -1px);font-weight:bold;width:20px;font-size:12px;line-height:20px;margin-right:10px;height:20px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">5</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">服务是否直接暴露在公网？</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果以上有两条命中，基本可以认定需要升级。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">写在最后</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是 React 生态近年来最严重的一次安全事件。影响范围大、触发条件简单，属于“只要部署就可能中招”的级别。如果你有线上项目跑在 React 19 或 Next.js App Router 上，请尽快完成升级。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">安全问题不能拖，这次尤其如此。</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "React Server Components 和 Next.js App Router 被曝出最高级别安全漏洞，允许未授权远程代码执行，需立即升级修复。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "React Server Components 和 Next.js App Router 被曝出最高级别安全漏洞，允许未授权远程代码执行，需立即升级修复。",
  "summary": "文章紧急通报了 React Server Components (RSC) 和 Next.js App Router 中发现的最高级别（CVSS 10）安全漏洞。该漏洞源于 RSC 在处理服务端请求时，对客户端数据的反序列化类型校验不严格，导致攻击者无需登录或权限，即可构造恶意请求，诱导服务器执行任意代码。文章详细列出了受影响的 React 19 部分版本和几乎所有基于 App Router 的 Next.js 版本（包括 15.x、16.x 及部分 14.3-canary 版本）。强调此漏洞的严重性在于其触发条件简单、影响范围广，且线上暴露接口的应用风险“默认存在”。文章明确指出，唯一的修复方式是立即升级到 React 和 Next.js 的最新补丁版本，不存在任何临时规避配置。最后提供了一个快速自查清单，并呼吁所有受影响的线上项目尽快完成升级，以避免潜在的安全风险。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "React 和 Next.js 中存在最高级别（CVSS 10）安全漏洞",
      "explanation": "该漏洞源于 RSC 反序列化时的类型校验不严格，允许攻击者在未授权情况下执行服务器端恶意代码，风险极高且影响广泛。"
    },
    {
      "point": "漏洞影响 React 19 及多数 Next.js App Router 版本",
      "explanation": "具体涉及 React Server Components 相关包和 Next.js 基于 App Router 的所有版本，使用 Pages Router 或未用 RSC 的项目风险较小。"
    },
    {
      "point": "唯一修复方式是立即升级到官方发布的补丁版本",
      "explanation": "官方明确指出没有任何配置可临时规避此漏洞，受影响用户必须尽快升级依赖到安全版本。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "React Server Components（RSC）出现了一个最高级别（CVSS 10）的安全漏洞。",
    "本次问题就出在这里——类型校验不严格，导致攻击者可以构造一个“伪 RSC 请求”，诱导服务器执行恶意代码。",
    "不需要登录，不需要权限，只要能请求到你的接口，就有可能直接执行服务器端代码。",
    "官方明确说了：没有任何配置可以临时规避漏洞，只能升级。",
    "这是 React 生态近年来最严重的一次安全事件。影响范围大、触发条件简单，属于“只要部署就可能中招”的级别。"
